data.description: Great LOCATION, great CURB APPEAL, great HOME! There are so many things to love about this home, beginning with the nicely landscaped front yard and welcoming covered front porch. The exceptional floor plan of this home includes a great use of storage, beautiful wood look luxury vinyl plank flooring in all areas with the exception of the bedrooms and loft. The spacious great room which is open to the kitchen & breakfast nook features LVP flooring, ceiling fan, large windows and a french door leading to the backyard. The well equipped kitchen comes with LVP flooring, a large center island, stainless appliance, pantry, plenty of espresso colored cabinetry and a breakfast bar. For more formal dining there is a beautiful dedicated dining room with LVP flooring and large window overlooking the front porch. Located on the lower level the split bedroom floor plan provides plenty of privacy for the master suite which includes an large bedroom with carpeted flooring, ceiling fan and large window. The master bath offers LVP flooring, double vanities, walk-in closet, a garden tub, separate walk-in shower and private water closet. There is also a powder room on the lower level with LVP flooring and pedestal sink. Upstairs you will find a HUGE loft area with carpeted flooring and recessed lighting and would make a great space for hosting football parties or homeschooling. The additional 4 bedrooms are all located on the 2nd floor and are all oversized with carpeted flooring and a tremendous amount of closet space. Rounding out the upper level is a full bath that features LVP flooring, double vanities and a tub/shower combo. The large laundry room with its' LVP flooring is conveniently located on the 2nd floor and includes existing shelving. The privacy fenced back yard with an open patio and artisan style fire pit is the perfect space for hosting backyard BBQ's and provides plenty of space for children's play equipment. This is a better than new home and is move in ready.
